{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "b2f0c7a5-3d2b-4c8f-a04b-6a7e9f1b2c3d",
		"name": "TaxVision - PaymentClient",
		"description": "Colección de pruebas del microservicio PaymentClient de TaxVision (cada tenant cobra a SUS propios clientes/taxpayers, modo DirectApiKeys o Stripe Connect). Usa el environment TaxVisionBackEnd (variable UrlBase apuntando al Gateway, p. ej. http://localhost:5047). Los endpoints bajo Config/Connect/Payments/Payouts/Recurring/PaymentLinks requieren TenantAdmin (o el rol con los permisos payment_client.* correspondientes); Admin requiere PlatformAdmin (payment_client.admin.cross_tenant). Webhooks y Checkout son públicos: los webhooks verifican HMAC (400 con firma dummy es el resultado esperado) y el checkout usa el token del PaymentLink como única prueba de posesión.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "PaymentLinks",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "CreatePaymentLink",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"const link = pm.response.json();\r",
									"if (link && link.id) {\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('paymentLinkId', link.id);\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('paymentLinkToken', link.token);\r",
									"    console.log('paymentLinkId:', link.id, '- token:', link.token);\r",
									"}\r"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"taxpayerId\": null,\n  \"amountCents\": 2500,\n  \"currency\": \"USD\",\n  \"purposeKind\": \"InvoicePayment\",\n  \"purposeExternalReferenceId\": \"inv-postman-001\",\n  \"expiration\": \"01:00:00\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-client/payment-links",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"payments-client",
								"payment-links"
							]
						},
						"description": "Crea un link magico de pago (§32.2). El token (32 bytes de RNG) es la unica prueba de posesion — no requiere cuenta ni JWT para canjearse. expiration en formato TimeSpan constante (hh:mm:ss). Requiere payment_client.payment_link.manage."
					},
					"response": []
				},
