				{
					"name": "ChargeTenantPayment - ZeroAmount (100% discount)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));\r",
									"\r",
									"const paymentId = pm.response.json();\r",
									"if (paymentId) {\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('zeroAmountTenantPaymentId', paymentId);\r",
									"    console.log('zeroAmountTenantPaymentId:', paymentId);\r",
									"}\r"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"providerCode\": \"Stripe\",\n  \"amountCents\": 0,\n  \"currency\": \"USD\",\n  \"taxpayerId\": null,\n  \"purposeKind\": \"InvoicePayment\",\n  \"purposeExternalReferenceId\": \"inv-postman-100pct-off\",\n  \"paymentMethodReference\": \"pm_card_visa\",\n  \"receiptEmail\": null,\n  \"idempotencyKey\": \"postman-zero-{{$guid}}\",\n  \"platformFeeAmountCents\": null,\n  \"platformFeeReference\": null\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-client/payments",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"payments-client",
								"payments"
							]
						},
						"description": "Un monto final de $0 (p.ej. un codigo de Growth al 100% de descuento) NUNCA debe llegar a Stripe -- un PaymentIntent de $0 es invalido para su API. TenantPayment.CreateAlreadySucceeded nace directo en Succeeded sin tocar el provider, tanto en modo DirectApiKeys como Connect. Prerrequisito: Config > CreateConfig + UpdateSecrets ya corridos para el tenant (config activo). Requiere payment_client.payment.charge. Devuelve el Guid del TenantPayment creado."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "GetTenantPayment - ZeroAmount (assert Succeeded, no provider touched)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));\r",
									"\r",
									"const payment = pm.response.json();\r",
									"pm.test('Payment succeeded without ever touching the provider', () => {\r",
									"    pm.expect(payment.status).to.eql('Succeeded');\r",
									"    pm.expect(payment.amountCents).to.eql(0);\r",
									"    pm.expect(payment.externalChargeReference).to.be.null;\r",
									"    pm.expect(payment.providerChargeReferenceOnConnect).to.be.null;\r",
									"    pm.expect(payment.failureCode).to.be.null;\r",
									"});\r"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-client/payments/{{zeroAmountTenantPaymentId}}",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"payments-client",
								"payments",
								"{{zeroAmountTenantPaymentId}}"
							]
						},
						"description": "Verifica el resultado del cobro de monto cero: debe quedar Succeeded de inmediato, sin ExternalChargeReference/ProviderChargeReferenceOnConnect ni FailureCode -- prueba de que ni Direct ni Connect llegaron a ejecutarse. Requiere payment_client.payment.read.\n\nNota: PaymentLink NO admite monto cero (PaymentLink.Create rechaza AmountCents<=0 por diseno, igual que TenantPayment.Create) -- un link de $0 nunca se puede crear, asi que ese camino no aplica y no se prueba aqui."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
