		{
			"name": "Negative Cases — Actor Type",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "CustomerPortal token rejected — SearchPaymentLinks",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{customerPortalAccessToken}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/payments-client/payment-links?page=1&pageSize=20",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"payments-client",
								"payment-links"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "page",
									"value": "1"
								},
								{
									"key": "pageSize",
									"value": "20"
								},
								{
									"key": "status",
									"value": "Active",
									"disabled": true
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Fase 7.3 (Actor_Type_Authorization_Layers_Plan.md) — caso negativo cross-actor. Mismo endpoint que \"SearchPaymentLinks\" (requiere payment_client.payment_link.read, actor type staff), llamado con {{customerPortalAccessToken}} (poblado por Portal Access > LoginCustomerPortal en la colección Customer). Debe rechazar con 403 — Capa 1 (HasPermission) y Capa 2 (AllowActorTypes) del mecanismo de autorización, ver el plan. No es exhaustivo endpoint por endpoint (ver ActorTypeAuthorizationFilterTests.cs para esa cobertura completa a nivel filtro); este caso documenta y ejercita el mecanismo real vía HTTP.\n\n---\nDescripción original: Lista los PaymentLinks del tenant autenticado. Requiere payment_client.payment_link.read."
					},
					"response": [],
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"pm.test(\"403 Forbidden — CustomerPortal actor type blocked from a staff-only endpoint\", () => {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(403);",
									"});"
								]
							}
						}
					]
				}
			],
			"description": "Fase 7.3 del plan de autorización por actor type — casos negativos runnable que confirman que un JWT de actor type equivocado recibe 403, no solo que el flujo correcto funciona. Ver Actor_Type_Authorization_Layers_Plan.md."
		}
	]
